company_name: STOLZENBERG HEIMTIER- UND BEDARFSGROSSHANDELSGES. MBH, VORMALS EDMUND MANN
information: The company STOLZENBERG HEIMTIER- UND BEDARFSGROSSHANDELSGES. MBH, VORMALS EDMUND MANN, is a Wholesaler, founded in 1947, which operates in the Pets industry. It is based in Mönchengladbach, Germany.
